I don't like "the other story" that's in this collection with the asshole older brother blackmailing and NTR his little sister (Sister Island is alot like this one abit, but I prefer this one over it). It reminded me of that other one EBA I think made that had the nerd older brother being oppressed by his gyaru little sister, but after the raping her to teach her a lesson, it's shown that he like the asshole in the story I mentioning brought it on himself! She caught him raiding and sniffing her panties, which made him a broken pedestal to her. Meaning her behavior to him early in the story was well deserved! I think it's because I like it when the girls "bring it on themselves" like this one and Sister Island. Can't stand the asshole wins trope sometimes! It gets old, cringy and unfappable (I can fap to GOOD doujin, bad ones...well I prefer reading their NENG)

Getting his GF back and beating him up! A sequel had him being more oppressed by the GF who is still pissed about the MC episode, so he decides once he gets it back to do her AND her mother...it ends with bully reversing it on him again, calling him an idiot for not learning the first time, but has GF and her Mom fuck him to a point he'll NEVER want to fuck a woman again! But yeah I always questioned why the MC Apps that aren't supernatural can't be used by the person who had his woman stolen to get her back and revenge. Hentai logic I guess....seriously their has to be a limit to abusing that! It's abuse like this which is why Mary/Marty Sue's reign
